{"tid":897991,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企無哂花生油 轉用面油煮野食得唔得？","createTime":"2018-11-11T11:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T13:11:49.000Z","uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62d3da8dbe1ad9957b2f91cd763e1bbc923b0a35","tid":897991,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:15:25.000Z","msg":"面上太多油<br />\n唔想哂 可唔可以拎來煮野食？"},{"pid":"6f91720bc19ae68001570c057d3577512df1da5e","tid":897991,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:20:55.000Z","msg":"唔得，用黎滑大腸就得"},{"pid":"baff036dd465095a629683905ffe7751f8750f23","tid":897991,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"諗起皆大歡喜祥仔"},{"pid":"1635c46bffa63c2716d6f80b176628bf649e5a6d","tid":897991,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:27:21.000Z","msg":"三酸甘油脂"},{"pid":"e20d3c5e8f042ddd7a1fe629d681b2bad1d82251","tid":897991,"uid":37,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:28:25.000Z","msg":"三酸甘油脂.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392f8bf16886f976ae5171f76a483bd334fcbe79","tid":897991,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:55:58.000Z","msg":"精油普遍存在於植物的各個部位，包括樹根、樹幹、樹皮、樹莖、葉、花、果實等部位。但實際上它並不只是油，是一種經光合作用而生成的有機化合物，是成分複雜的芳香植物族。精油對植物的生長扮演重要的角色，除了具備調節溫度和預防疾病的功能外，還能保護植物免受細菌及病菌的侵害。另外，花瓣中的精油，可吸引對自己有益的昆蟲靠近，同時也能避免對自己有害的昆蟲接近，所以人們利用精油的這項特質在生活中驅逐害蟲以及保健身體。但特殊氣味也會吸引特定的蟲害。"},{"pid":"ed2c2a91399c51d14bbe303a4191339c4c5e562c","tid":897991,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T13:01:05.000Z","msg":"伊藤"},{"pid":"1ff49562436cf055e66243f530ee86be7c0093b2","tid":897991,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=3okb8no/qq90007s715n9s9o40n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3okb8no%2Fqq90007s715n9s9o40n.jpg&h=0088d8bc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}